import React from 'react'
import { Button, Container, Row, Col, Form } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { Router, Link } from '@reach/router'

function Issueslist() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Form>
                <hr />
                <Form.Group as={Row} >
                    <Form.Label column sm="2">
                        Title
                    </Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="10">
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Title" name="title" />
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Row} >
                    <Form.Label column sm="2">Description</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="10">
                     </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
                    <Col sm="2"></Col>
                    <Col sm="10">
                        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" name="checkbox" />
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <hr />
                <Row>
                <Col sm="6">
                <Form.Group as={Row} >
                    <Form.Label column sm="4">Assignee</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="8">
                    <Form.Control as="select" placeholder="Assignee" name="assignee" >
                        <option>Unassigned</option>
                        <option>Ranjith</option>
                    </Form.Control>
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                </Col>
                </Row>
                <hr />
            <Button variant="success" >Submit issue</Button>
            </Form>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Issueslist
